[[File:LEGODartBoard.jpg|thumb|right|A [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] playing darts]]
The game of '''darts''' was a game played by throwing pointed darts at a circular game board, which could be hung on a wall. The darts would be thrown at the bright dart board, and where they would land determined the score the player received. Sometimes, when a dart missed the board, it would embed itself in the surrounding wall. In a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]], a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] could be seen playing darts.

==Behind the scenes==
The game of darts appeared in ''[[LEGO Star Wars: Revenge of the Brick]]''.

